description:
&lt;p&gt;There is an opportunity to join Northumbria Healthcare NHS Foundation Trusts Digital Services Team as an Application Support Specialist to support the efficient operation of the clinical IT applications such as PAS, ICE and System One throughout the Trust.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder will join the Applications Management Team and will work closely with clinical practitioners and application specialists to co-ordinate the implementation, development and on-going support of the trust’s clinical IT applications to deliver maximum benefits for our patients.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Essential Criteria:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for someone who has the following skills;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- Formal qualification at Degree level or equivalent level of knowledge acquired by in depth experience of using or managing business or clinical applications.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- Must be able to communicate effectively with all levels of users.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- Experience of IT technologies.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- Knowledge of Microsoft Office and Windows&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- Must be able to work without close supervision&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- Candidates will be expected to have a good level of general IT literacy but the successful candidate will receive full training in using the clinical and business systems and you will quickly gain excellent systems knowledge to drive on-going development.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- The applicant will have good interpersonal skills and be a team player who can deliver quality outcomes to agreed timescales.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;The successful post holder must be able to role model compassionate and inclusive leadership in order to shape the creation of a collective leadership culture within the Trust. &lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Closing Date: 18th November 2020&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Paul James&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Application Management Team Leader&lt;/p&gt;
